{"tid":2463646,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國的秘密營地 消失的新疆維吾爾人都遭遇了什麼？","createTime":"2021-03-27T01:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T04:54:17.000Z","uid":224066,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d11edb82ac2c531de44ce7a78df07e9b851be4b4","tid":2463646,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:13:55.000Z","msg":"2015年7月12日，一顆衛星在中國廣袤的西部沙漠和綠洲城鎮上空盤旋。<br />\n<br />\n當天拍攝的照片顯示，這裡只是一片人跡罕至的灰白色荒漠。<br />\n<br />\n這個調查開始的地方不同尋常，它涉及其中一個我們這個時代最緊迫的人權問題。<br />\n<br />\n2018年4月22日，即在三年不到的時間裡，同一片沙漠上空拍攝的衛星照片顯示了一些新的東西。<br />\n<br />\n一個面積巨大、保安嚴密的建築呈現在眼前。<br />\n<br />\n它的外牆長約兩公里，四周矗立著16座瞭望塔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/resources/idt-sh/China_hidden_camps_chinese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Fresources%2Fidt-sh%2FChina_hidden_camps_chinese&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWrBzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=b7b788ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Fresources%2Fidt-sh%2FChina_hidden_camps_chinese&h=4c6ca045\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/resources/idt-sh/China_hidden_camps_chinese</a>"},{"pid":"d4bd3bbe87a0d6d92dabbfb259f63b1cec25d9d9","tid":2463646,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:25:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d277ee097e7652a491eb148322ea9d0afd173b5","tid":2463646,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"好詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba39c48e651bd7f52bc281c100d820206cf83722","tid":2463646,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"2002年，熱依拉．阿不來提（Reyila Abulaiti）從新疆到英國求學。<br />\n<br />\n她遇到一個英國人，嫁給了他，取得了英國公民身份並組建家庭。<br />\n<br />\n去年，她的母親謝姆西努爾．皮達（Xiamuxinuer Pida）像往常夏天一樣來到英國，和她的女兒及孫子一起在倫敦觀光。<br />\n<br />\n66歲的謝姆西努爾是一名受過良好教育的前工程師，她曾在一家中國國企任職多年。<br />\n<br />\n她於6月2日飛回新疆。<br />\n<br />\n由於沒有聽到媽媽的消息，熱依拉打電話詢問母親是否平安到家。<br />\n<br />\n這段對話簡短但恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n「她告訴我，警察正在搜查房子，」熱依拉回憶說。<br />\n<br />\n警方搜查的目標似乎正是熱依拉。<br />\n<br />\n她的母親說，警方要求熱依拉提供一些文件的影印本，包括英國地址證明、英國護照影印本、英國電話號碼和大學課程資料。<br />\n<br />\n後來，在熱依拉的母親要求她透過中國手機聊天軟件發送這些資料後，她的母親說了一句讓她覺得脊椎發涼的話。<br />\n<br />\n「別再打電話給我了，」她的母親告訴她。「永遠不要再打給我。」<br />\n<br />\n這是女兒最後一次聽到母親的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n她相信，從那以後母親就一直在營地裡。<br />\n<br />\n「我的媽媽無緣無故被拘留了，」她說。「據我所知，中國政府希望將維吾爾人的身份從世界上抹除。」"},{"pid":"5c5533db33164515e92fb391846c5731e0d5abab","tid":2463646,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187a8a7f4ee71e9c63219acf1b9cf2c4b61ee987","tid":2463646,"uid":249866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79e7fd5ce913f1749ada7cc3cb53eaeabc1679d","tid":2463646,"uid":143402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"其實你哋真係信新疆有「種族滅絕」咩? （2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2463475/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2463475/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd000598cccf7bbac1d7fac594bb003568cd973","tid":2463646,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:42:12.000Z","msg":"好聞要推"},{"pid":"ed97746e6ed0237dfdd95e49d3821b4754d1d35e","tid":2463646,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e47dae8c4094fb0fae1b7ffebc581432dcb6e82","tid":2463646,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfa6cf3bdf19094243d6e754576c3b0538bd41d","tid":2463646,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:54:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}